  "body": "- [ ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nI can't deploy the [collateral contract](https://github.com/ripio/rcn-network/blob/rcn_burner/contracts/core/diaspore/cosigner/Collateral.sol), ganache-cli give me `VM Exception while processing transaction: out of gas`\r\n\r\nIf start ganache-cli with `--allowUnlimitedContractSize true` the deploy works, and can log the deployedBytecode length:\r\n   ```console.log(collateral.constructor._json.bytecode.length); // 49478```\r\nand the gasUsed:\r\n```console.log((await web3.eth.getTransactionReceipt(collateral.transactionHash)).gasUsed); // 6808544```\r\n\r\nI think the optimizer its not on when use `truffle test` but in the [truffle config](https://github.com/ripio/rcn-network/blob/rcn_burner/truffle.js) have:\r\n```\r\n...\r\n            settings: {\r\n                optimizer: {\r\n                    enabled: true,\r\n                    runs: 200,\r\n                },\r\n                evmVersion: 'constantinople',\r\n            },\r\n...\r\n```\r\nI can deploy the [collateral contract](https://github.com/ripio/rcn-network/blob/rcn_burner/contracts/core/diaspore/cosigner/Collateral.sol) in remix with optimizer on \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nClone the repo: `git clone https://github.com/ripio/rcn-network.git`\r\nOn terminal: \r\n```\r\ncd rcn-network\r\ngit checkout rcn_burner\r\nnpm install\r\nnode_modules/.bin/ganache-cli --gasLimit 7000000\r\n```\r\nIn other terminal:\r\n```\r\nnode_modules/.bin/truffle test\r\n```\r\nCan check the error in circleci [test](https://circleci.com/gh/ripio/rcn-network/4262?utm_campaign=vcs-integration-link&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=github-build-link)\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nDeploy the collateral contract and test it.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nReturn this exception: `VM Exception while processing transaction: out of gas`\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Repo: [rcn_burner branch](https://github.com/ripio/rcn-network/tree/rcn_burner)\r\n* Operating System: Linux\r\n* Truffle version: v5.0.24 (core: 5.0.24)\r\n* Solidity version: - 0.5.8 (solc-js)\r\n* node version: v11.5.0\r\n* Web3.js version: v1.0.0-beta.37\r\n* npm version: 6.4.1\r\n* ganache-cli version: Ganache CLI v6.4.3 (ganache-core: 2.5.5)",
